00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:31,060
Be careful on your way.

260
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:37,700
Slave combat. Always exciting everyday.

261
00:21:37,700 --> 00:21:39,200
Remember to go.

262
00:21:42,400 --> 00:21:44,000
Here. Have one.

263
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:48,600
Hey!

264
00:21:49,400 --> 00:21:51,400
- That...<br>- What?

265
00:21:51,400 --> 00:21:54,000
This... Is this a fat guy?

266
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:55,400
That's right.

267
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:58,600
By his side, is there still a slightly taller and thinner guy?

268
00:21:58,600 --> 00:21:59,600
That's right.

269
00:22:00,600 --> 00:22:03,000
Can you take me to see them?

270
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:05,000
Based on what?

271
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:06,500
Look.

272
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:10,100
Here. Take it.

273
00:22:10,100 --> 00:22:12,100
Take me to see your boss. Okay?

274
00:22:20,480 --> 00:22:23,730
Hey, meal time! Meal time!

275
00:22:24,210 --> 00:22:26,310
Woah!

276
00:22:29,650 --> 00:22:31,810
Hurry and eat. Tomorrow, it's up to you guys.

277
00:22:31,810 --> 00:22:33,690
Wow!

278
00:22:33,690 --> 00:22:35,570
Has the sky changed? How come they are being so nice?

279
00:22:35,630 --> 00:22:38,320
- There's even a drumstick.<br>- Earlier I heard them talking about something...

280
00:22:38,360 --> 00:22:43,020
He seems to have said that if this drumstick was cooked for an hour more, it might taste better.

281
00:22:43,500 --> 00:22:45,230
How come you only know how to eat?

282
00:22:45,240 --> 00:22:46,300
Or else what?

283
00:22:46,300 --> 00:22:50,230
They were talking about... about... seeing what our fate will be tomorrow.

284
00:22:50,790 --> 00:22:52,660
What does it mean?

285
00:22:54,360 --> 00:22:56,430
Don't know.

286
00:22:57,230 --> 00:22:59,200
- This drumstick...<br>- No...

287
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:02,090
No. We don't want it.

288
00:23:02,880 --> 00:23:04,320
What's going on?

289
00:23:04,370 --> 00:23:06,380
i don't know.

290
00:23:06,390 --> 00:23:09,220
While there is a drumstick, just hurry and eat it.

291
00:23:09,220 --> 00:23:11,960
The people in here have not eaten any drumstick yet.

292
00:23:11,960 --> 00:23:12,970
Why?

293
00:23:12,970 --> 00:23:14,970
Aren't there chicken drumsticks in the kitchen?

294
00:23:14,970 --> 00:23:17,630
The chicken drumsticks in the kitchen are for the Power King.

295
00:23:17,630 --> 00:23:21,300
- Ha?<br>- Only people who are fighting with him get to have a drumstick.

296
00:23:21,330 --> 00:23:23,420
It's just that...

297
00:23:24,360 --> 00:23:25,500
It's just that what?

298
00:23:25,530 --> 00:23:28,350
Hurry and say it. How come you stopped midway?

299
00:23:28,910 --> 00:23:32,740
It's just that people who have eaten a chicken drumstick have never returned.

300
00:23:33,250 --> 00:23:34,330
Never returned?

301
00:23:34,330 --> 00:23:37,430
Older Bro Fei, does it mean we can get out?

302
00:23:37,900 --> 00:23:42,820
Never returning means we have to forever stay in the arena.

303
00:23:50,870 --> 00:23:52,780
How can this be called a chicken drumstick?

304
00:23:52,800 --> 00:23:55,900
This is totally arsenic.

305
00:23:56,730 --> 00:23:58,230
It's not even as good as arsenic.

306
00:23:58,240 --> 00:24:01,270
If you die because of eating arsenic, you don't even need to get beaten up before dying.

307
00:24:02,100 --> 00:24:06,460
Let me out! Let me out!

308
00:24:08,410 --> 00:24:10,080
I still don't want to die.

309
00:24:10,130 --> 00:24:12,560
Older Bro Fei, I still want to live longer.

310
00:24:12,560 --> 00:24:14,730
I still want to eat lots of food.

311
00:24:14,740 --> 00:24:17,350
I still don't want to die!

312
00:24:17,370 --> 00:24:19,440
Stop being noisy already.

313
00:24:19,470 --> 00:24:21,150
You won't die.

314
00:24:22,440 --> 00:24:25,440
Older Bro Fei. Older Bro Fei.

315
00:24:25,470 --> 00:24:28,590
You are so smart so you must have an idea already, right?

316
00:24:36,340 --> 00:24:37,820
How come it's so few?

317
00:24:37,840 --> 00:24:39,280
These are 500 liang.

318
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:43,060
We worked hard for 2 months. Once we divide this among us, it's not even enough to buy a woman.

319
00:24:43,060 --> 00:24:44,900
Didn't we already agree to sell them for 900 liang?

320
00:24:44,900 --> 00:24:46,060
How come there is only 500 liang?

321
00:24:46,060 --> 00:24:48,360
Only 500 liang?

322
00:24:51,110 --> 00:24:56,770
Captain, our buddies are complaining that their share is quite few.

323
00:24:57,410 --> 00:24:59,580
What do you mean?

324
00:25:00,360 --> 00:25:02,570
Some people are saying...

325
00:25:06,130 --> 00:25:08,870
that you personally pocketed the money.

326
00:25:13,170 --> 00:25:14,920
I, Cheng Ming Pan,

327
00:25:14,950 --> 00:25:17,180
am not that kind of person.

328
00:25:18,100 --> 00:25:21,900
I know that with captain's character, you won't do such things.

329
00:25:21,920 --> 00:25:25,730
But our buddies just want an explanation.

330
00:25:25,750 --> 00:25:29,380
How come the money we got this time is so few?

331
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:31,190
Right.

332
00:25:40,090 --> 00:25:41,610
I know.

333
00:25:41,610 --> 00:25:44,160
I know that you all are discontented.

334
00:25:45,900 --> 00:25:48,450
You found a captain and followed him

335
00:25:48,450 --> 00:25:53,130
just for him to bear the responsibility that you all can't bear and to make appropriate decisions!

336
00:25:53,130 --> 00:25:55,780
So as to preserve your own interest.

337
00:25:56,550 --> 00:26:00,950
In this world, only money and power are most realistic.

338
00:26:01,460 --> 00:26:04,240
Money may be lost

339
00:26:04,250 --> 00:26:07,670
but power will never be lost.

340
00:26:08,230 --> 00:26:10,500
Let me tell you.

341
00:26:10,530 --> 00:26:13,740
What others can't do, I can do.

342
00:26:13,740 --> 00:26:17,630
What others can't defeat, I can defeat.

343
00:26:17,640 --> 00:26:20,190
If I say that I can't do it,

344
00:26:21,800 --> 00:26:24,160
then on this island,

345
00:26:24,620 --> 00:26:27,180
none can do it.

346
00:26:31,840 --> 00:26:33,750
Let's go.

347
00:26:34,500 --> 00:26:37,010
You people let go of me! Let go of me!

348
00:26:37,030 --> 00:26:38,710
- Are you blind?!<br>- Who is this?

349
00:26:38,710 --> 00:26:41,850
Captain, we picked him up on the beach two days ago.

350
00:26:46,870 --> 00:26:49,710
Let's try to get along. Let's try to get along.

351
00:26:49,730 --> 00:26:53,310
This... Who is the one paying for all these?

352
00:26:56,220 --> 00:26:57,520
Ladies, go disperse now.

353
00:26:57,520 --> 00:26:58,990
Disperse. Disperse.

354
00:26:58,990 --> 00:27:00,790
Go. Let's go.

355
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:03,590
He is a Toyo man.

356
00:27:03,590 --> 00:27:06,290
You all know that I am a Toyo man and do you still treat me like this?

357
00:27:06,340 --> 00:27:08,290
You all will die tragically!

358
00:27:08,290 --> 00:27:11,400
- Come! Throw him into the ocean to feed the fishes!<br>- Yes!

359
00:27:11,420 --> 00:27:15,300
- Get up!<br>- Wait! Wait! Wait!

360
00:27:15,330 --> 00:27:18,480
I can tell you all a chance to get rich.

361
00:27:18,500 --> 00:27:20,550
A chance to get super rich.

362
00:27:20,550 --> 00:27:23,930
It is 100 times more than the money you earn right now.

363
00:27:28,130 --> 00:27:29,340
You all leave.

364
00:27:29,340 --> 00:27:30,690
Yes!

365
00:27:35,760 --> 00:27:37,600
Come. Sit. Sit.

366
00:27:42,150 --> 00:27:44,290
Let me tell you.

367
00:27:44,290 --> 00:27:47,390
On a mysterious small island,

368
00:27:51,110 --> 00:27:55,480
there is a very valuable treasure that's worth several cities.

369
00:28:00,800 --> 00:28:02,880
- Are you talking about the Money Island?<br>- That's right.

370
00:28:02,910 --> 00:28:05,320
The legend of Money Island is known even by a three-year-old child.

371
00:28:05,320 --> 00:28:08,800
Did you think I'd believe it?

372
00:28:08,800 --> 00:28:11,230
It's up to you to believe it or not.

373
00:28:11,260 --> 00:28:12,930
Everyone does know about it,

374
00:28:12,930 --> 00:28:16,400
but who really went to find it? Think about it.

375
00:28:17,010 --> 00:28:20,050
Don't be rash. Listen to me.

376
00:28:21,040 --> 00:28:25,650
We Toyo warriors believe one saying the most.

377
00:28:25,650 --> 00:28:29,560
Chance is given to people who loves to take risks.

378
00:28:29,570 --> 00:28:34,750
Think about it. Did I endured numerous dangers and hardships to come here

379
00:28:34,800 --> 00:28:37,740
just because of a legend?

380
00:28:37,740 --> 00:28:40,990
I am thinking on your behalf.

381
00:28:40,990 --> 00:28:43,200
I am giving you a chance.

382
00:28:43,200 --> 00:28:44,510
Look at those sailors of yours.

383
00:28:44,510 --> 00:28:46,650
They only see money.

384
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:49,660
Without money, you don't even get the power to rule them.

385
00:28:49,680 --> 00:28:53,240
I'm afraid your captain position might be hard to keep.

386
00:28:53,260 --> 00:28:55,370
You can choose not to believe what I'm saying.

387
00:28:55,390 --> 00:28:57,250
Go to the island and ask about it.

388
00:28:57,260 --> 00:29:00,040
There surely is someone who knows this secret.

389
00:29:00,060 --> 00:29:02,990
It's just that they won't tell you.

390
00:29:03,480 --> 00:29:06,150
Won't share it with you.

391
00:29:07,380 --> 00:29:09,950
What you are talking about is...

392
00:29:09,950 --> 00:29:11,710
Ming Zhen?

393
00:29:12,610 --> 00:29:14,630
Smart.

394
00:29:17,320 --> 00:29:20,110
Just because you say that they are your friends,

395
00:29:20,130 --> 00:29:22,720
you are asking me to let them go.

396
00:29:22,730 --> 00:29:26,240
Little child, you are too naive.

397
00:29:27,610 --> 00:29:31,900
In this world, there are no free things.

398
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:37,150
Okay. Then you tell me. In what way will you set them free?

399
00:29:37,170 --> 00:29:39,050
Very simple.

400
00:29:39,050 --> 00:29:41,550
Everything in here are merchandise.

401
00:29:42,390 --> 00:29:44,710
As long as you are able to have enough of that,*<br>(* money)

402
00:29:44,730 --> 00:29:47,410
you can take anyone away.

403
00:29:48,730 --> 00:29:50,330
You want money, is that it?

404
00:29:50,340 --> 00:29:53,080
Okay. How much?

405
00:29:53,820 --> 00:29:56,790
Let's not first talk about money.

406
00:29:56,850 --> 00:29:59,210
This little fatty

407
00:29:59,230 --> 00:30:01,530
is currently loved by the audience.

408
00:30:01,530 --> 00:30:04,030
He is my precious.

409
00:30:06,050 --> 00:30:08,530
I really kind of can't bear to let him go.

410
00:30:09,340 --> 00:30:11,640
Didn't you say that if I have the money, you will let them go?

411
00:30:11,650 --> 00:30:14,020
Just say it. How much money do you want?

412
00:30:16,230 --> 00:30:18,780
Can you see this box?

413
00:30:18,780 --> 00:30:21,660
In it is all the betting money.

414
00:30:21,660 --> 00:30:25,680
During the competition, this money will grow more and more.

415
00:30:25,700 --> 00:30:30,770
As long as by that time, you can give me twice the amount,

416
00:30:30,790 --> 00:30:32,360
you can take the people away.

417
00:30:32,380 --> 00:30:35,170
You clearly don't want to set them free!

418
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:38,570
If you won't accept it, I won't try to force you.

419
00:30:42,560 --> 00:30:44,410
Okay.

420
00:30:44,430 --> 00:30:46,540
I accept it.

421
00:30:46,540 --> 00:30:48,560
But you must first let me see them.

422
00:30:49,690 --> 00:30:51,830
They, you can't.

423
00:30:51,830 --> 00:30:54,260
Just seeing one, you can.

424
00:30:54,700 --> 00:30:57,360
Pull that little fatty up here.

425
00:30:57,380 --> 00:30:59,290
Yes!

426
00:30:59,320 --> 00:31:07,010
KoreanDramaX.co

427
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:15,190
Miss. Miss.

428
00:31:15,190 --> 00:31:16,630
Miss, wake up.

429
00:31:16,630 --> 00:31:18,260
It's time to eat.

430
00:31:27,100 --> 00:31:28,620
What is your name?

431
00:31:28,660 --> 00:31:30,290
My name is Ah Chang.

432
00:31:30,310 --> 00:31:32,230
Ah Chang?

433
00:31:34,060 --> 00:31:36,160
My foot seemed wounded.

434
00:31:36,180 --> 00:31:38,480
Do you have any medicine?

435
00:31:38,510 --> 00:31:41,080
These exact medicines I have will be useful.

436
00:31:41,090 --> 00:31:43,060
Being a woman and going on fights outside,

437
00:31:43,080 --> 00:31:45,190
why didn't you prepare some medicines?

438
00:31:45,200 --> 00:31:47,450
You really are very considerate.

439
00:31:48,930 --> 00:31:51,240
That who, has my Younger Sis eaten yet?

440
00:31:51,240 --> 00:31:52,540
She still hasn't.

441
00:31:52,540 --> 00:31:54,340
What is this thing?

442
00:31:54,340 --> 00:31:55,640
Her foot is injured.

443
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:57,770
I brought her some medicine.

444
00:31:58,890 --> 00:32:01,580
You are quite considerate.

445
00:32:01,590 --> 00:32:04,130
- Leave first.<br>- Yes.

446
00:32:04,930 --> 00:32:06,380
What really are you planning to do to me?

447
00:32:06,380 --> 00:32:08,920
You are my precious treasure.

448
00:32:08,980 --> 00:32:11,410
How can I bear to do anything to you?

449
00:32:11,410 --> 00:32:14,240
I am even hoping for you to earn money for me.

450
00:32:15,560 --> 00:32:18,470
By that time, the two of us can be rich.

451
00:32:18,480 --> 00:32:20,190
Once we divide the money,

452
00:32:20,190 --> 00:32:22,770
wandering the ends of the world and travelling around the world,

453
00:32:22,790 --> 00:32:27,090
who would be willing to stay in this god-forsaken and inhumane island?

454
00:32:27,110 --> 00:32:31,230
Let me tell you. I will never do any of those things you are telling me to do.

455
00:32:31,250 --> 00:32:32,790
You better just give up on this idea.

456
00:32:32,790 --> 00:32:34,670
Younger Sister,

457
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:37,280
a person should learn to be grateful.

458
00:32:37,310 --> 00:32:38,710
If not because I saved you,

459
00:32:38,710 --> 00:32:41,560
you already don't know where you're at now.

460
00:32:42,290 --> 00:32:45,800
I even give you good food and drinks everyday.

461
00:32:46,490 --> 00:32:49,080
Why don't you just let me work in the kitchen?

462
00:32:51,550 --> 00:32:56,370
Will I let a beautiful lady work in the kitchen?

463
00:32:56,370 --> 00:32:57,590
Am I insane?

464
00:32:57,610 --> 00:32:59,480
You are indeed insane.

465
00:33:00,790 --> 00:33:03,030
Younger Sister,

466
00:33:06,060 --> 00:33:08,600
just listen to my advice.

467
00:33:08,620 --> 00:33:10,470
Just do your job well.

468
00:33:10,470 --> 00:33:14,660
You tell me, you are just staying in this place everyday, what can you do?

469
00:33:14,680 --> 00:33:16,860
Listen to me.

470
00:33:16,860 --> 00:33:21,990
I guarantee that your future life will have endless glory and wealth.

471
00:33:30,630 --> 00:33:33,250
These are all high quality cosmetics.

472
00:33:33,280 --> 00:33:34,730
Style yourself well.

473
00:33:34,730 --> 00:33:37,460
You must be beautiful.

474
00:33:37,460 --> 00:33:40,190
A woman... should be beautiful.

475
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:41,790
As long as you are beautiful,

476
00:33:41,790 --> 00:33:43,970
let's talk about some other things.

477
00:33:43,970 --> 00:33:46,980
I thank Older Sister for saving me.

478
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:50,180
But for the matter you want me to do, I can't do it.

479
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:58,030
Too bad, it's not up to you.

480
00:33:58,030 --> 00:34:00,490
Such a pretty lady,

481
00:34:00,490 --> 00:34:04,260
that even my heart flutters just by looking at you.

482
00:34:05,810 --> 00:34:07,760
Not just five years ago,

483
00:34:07,760 --> 00:34:11,620
even 10 years ago, my skin isn't as good as yours.

484
00:34:11,630 --> 00:34:13,910
Really so envious.

485
00:34:16,220 --> 00:34:19,540
I am giving you one chance to get the top beauty position.

486
00:34:19,590 --> 00:34:22,420
Once you have decided, tell it to me.

487
00:34:23,430 --> 00:34:24,860
Let's go.

488
00:34:30,380 --> 00:34:33,710
<i>I don't know where Bai Ze and the others are right now.</i>

489
00:34:35,180 --> 00:34:37,250
<i>How come I still am thinking about them?</i>

490
00:34:37,940 --> 00:34:40,220
<i>They have no relations with me at all.</i>

491
00:34:44,160 --> 00:34:45,760
- Get over there.<br>- Bai Ze!

492
00:34:45,760 --> 00:34:48,250
- Yuan Shuai!<br>- Move away!

493
00:34:49,630 --> 00:34:51,560
Yuan Shuai, how are you and Xiong Fei?

494
00:34:51,570 --> 00:34:53,180
We both are doing good.

495
00:34:53,180 --> 00:34:55,980
I thought that I would never be able to see you anymore.

496
00:34:56,020 --> 00:34:59,150
It's all my fault. I don't have the ability to save you from those human traffickers.

497
00:34:59,150 --> 00:35:00,540
Why must you still say all this now?

498
00:35:00,560 --> 00:35:02,340
We all have no freedom to act independently now.

499
00:35:02,370 --> 00:35:04,330
Have you found A Ji Ya?

500
00:35:04,820 --> 00:35:06,090
Not yet.

501
00:35:06,130 --> 00:35:07,500
I plan to save you and Xiong Fei first

502
00:35:07,500 --> 00:35:09,230
and then let's look for A Ji Ya together.

503
00:35:09,230 --> 00:35:11,180
- Okay.<br>- Enough already.

504
00:35:11,200 --> 00:35:14,930
You already saw the person and talked to him.

505
00:35:14,940 --> 00:35:17,000
Just think of a way to gather the money now.

506
00:35:17,010 --> 00:35:18,500
Take him away.

507
00:35:18,500 --> 00:35:19,580
Go!

508
00:35:19,580 --> 00:35:21,880
Wait for me! Once I'm able to come up with the money, I surely will come back to save you!

509
00:35:21,910 --> 00:35:23,470
If something bad happens to me and Older Bro Fei,

510
00:35:23,470 --> 00:35:27,430
help me tell Thirteenth Older Sis that we are having a good life in a far away place.

511
00:35:27,460 --> 00:35:29,890
We will forever miss her!

512
00:35:29,890 --> 00:35:32,340
- Remember!<br>- Stop saying nonsense!

513
00:35:34,450 --> 00:35:36,190
Hey!

514
00:35:36,200 --> 00:35:38,380
I will surely bring you the money before the competition starts.

515
00:35:38,380 --> 00:35:40,300
But you must not hurt my friends.

516
00:35:40,340 --> 00:35:42,660
I believe you.

517
00:35:42,670 --> 00:35:44,450
Go now.

518
00:35:59,070 --> 00:36:01,700
<i>Your sailors only see money.</i>

519
00:36:01,700 --> 00:36:03,910
<i>Without money, you don't even get the power to rule them.</i>

520
00:36:03,920 --> 00:36:06,710
<i>Your captain position won't be stable.</i>

521
00:36:17,980 --> 00:36:20,290
Captain, our boss is here.

522
00:36:23,670 --> 00:36:26,000
- You can leave now.<br>- Yes.

523
00:36:31,630 --> 00:36:34,890
It's so late already. Captain wants to see me for what reasons?

524
00:36:42,300 --> 00:36:45,040
Actually, we can work together.

525
00:36:46,140 --> 00:36:47,360
How?

526
00:36:47,380 --> 00:36:52,030
I know. You have stayed the longest here on this island.

527
00:36:52,050 --> 00:36:55,460
You surely know where the treasure is.

528
00:36:56,360 --> 00:37:00,180
Even a three-year-old child knows that there is no treasure on this island.

529
00:37:06,490 --> 00:37:09,990
Let me tell you. This island...

530
00:37:10,960 --> 00:37:14,100
I have the greatest strength.

531
00:37:14,100 --> 00:37:16,680
If you won't tell me the location of the treasure,

532
00:37:16,700 --> 00:37:20,360
I am making an oath that I will let you have nothing.

533
00:37:20,370 --> 00:37:23,320
If you really feel that this island has a treasure,

534
00:37:23,360 --> 00:37:25,010
then just go look for it yourself.

535
00:37:25,040 --> 00:37:27,650
If you find it, it's all yours.

536
00:37:27,650 --> 00:37:29,940
I don't want any of it.

537
00:37:29,980 --> 00:37:31,550
Okay.

538
00:37:31,570 --> 00:37:34,420
You're not saying the truth, is that it?

539
00:37:34,430 --> 00:37:37,170
Just you wait then.

540
00:38:04,790 --> 00:38:06,530
Miss, are you better?

541
00:38:06,560 --> 00:38:08,290
I'm better.

542
00:38:08,640 --> 00:38:12,350
- You... are Ah Chang, right?<br>- Right.

543
00:38:13,420 --> 00:38:15,640
Do you have a family?

544
00:38:17,940 --> 00:38:22,960
Ah Chang, those... I'm giving them to you. Give them to your wife.

545
00:38:24,700 --> 00:38:28,650
I am just a food server. I don't have any family.

546
00:38:28,660 --> 00:38:30,020
What's the meaning of that?!

547
00:38:30,020 --> 00:38:32,970
Who says that a food server can't have any family of their own?

548
00:38:32,980 --> 00:38:38,420
Ah Chang, have you thought about living a new kind of life?

549
00:38:39,400 --> 00:38:42,520
You go to work outside while she is at home washing clothes,

550
00:38:42,520 --> 00:38:45,320
cooking, and raising your children.

551
00:38:45,330 --> 00:38:50,030
When you go home, there will be warm dishes waiting for you to eat.

552
00:38:50,530 --> 00:38:53,860
When you are doing nothing, you all go out to stroll the town,

553
00:38:53,890 --> 00:38:55,640
to watch plays,

554
00:38:55,650 --> 00:38:58,260
to do anything that you want to do.

555
00:39:01,260 --> 00:39:05,760
Ah Chang, why must you let yourself suffer by staying here?

556
00:39:05,780 --> 00:39:10,510
Isn't Sakai like you, wanting to escape this place and live a more wonderful life?

557
00:39:10,520 --> 00:39:12,770
How come you won't?

558
00:39:37,290 --> 00:39:39,100
- Come with me.<br>- Ah Chang, you...

559
00:39:39,100 --> 00:39:41,230
Don't say anything anymore. Come with me.

560
00:39:48,230 --> 00:39:49,890
Hurry.

561
00:39:51,270 --> 00:39:53,110
Here.

562
00:39:53,940 --> 00:39:55,600
Hurry.

563
00:40:03,050 --> 00:40:05,990
Stop! Stop!

564
00:40:11,990 --> 00:40:14,600
What time is it?

565
00:40:14,630 --> 00:40:17,300
Will you still let people sleep?

566
00:40:18,700 --> 00:40:21,530
Not even choosing a good time to escape...

567
00:40:25,770 --> 00:40:29,160
- I'm begging you already. Just let me borrow the money.<br>- No.

568
00:40:29,170 --> 00:40:32,200
Before it was because I saw you wander into here

569
00:40:32,220 --> 00:40:34,090
and were being chased, I felt you were quite pitiful

570
00:40:34,090 --> 00:40:35,110
so I helped you.

571
00:40:35,120 --> 00:40:36,820
I already gave you extreme benevolence and did my utmost duty.

572
00:40:36,820 --> 00:40:38,370
Don't dare ask for more.

573
00:40:38,370 --> 00:40:39,560
Believe me.

574
00:40:39,560 --> 00:40:42,400
Just loan me the money first, I will definitely pay it back.

575
00:40:46,820 --> 00:40:49,060
You are just talking and not showing me anything to hold on to.

576
00:40:49,060 --> 00:40:51,090
How can I believe you?

577
00:40:51,120 --> 00:40:53,030
Actually, I am the capital's...

578
00:40:53,800 --> 00:40:57,150
I went out to sea this time because I have to do an important mission.

579
00:40:57,150 --> 00:40:59,190
Who would have thought that we would encounter a sea disaster midway,

580
00:40:59,210 --> 00:41:00,810
my friends and I got separated.

581
00:41:00,810 --> 00:41:03,500
I am borrowing money in order to save them.

582
00:41:03,980 --> 00:41:04,930
How about this?

583
00:41:04,930 --> 00:41:06,120
As long as I can go back,

584
00:41:06,120 --> 00:41:08,290
I'll immediately send men to bring you the money.

585
00:41:10,710 --> 00:41:13,050
If I believe everything that I hear,

586
00:41:13,060 --> 00:41:14,940
I won't be able to live up to now.

587
00:41:14,960 --> 00:41:16,080
You must know.

588
00:41:16,080 --> 00:41:20,950
In this world, no one is duty bound to help you.

589
00:41:21,330 --> 00:41:23,480
Okay. Then tell me.

590
00:41:23,480 --> 00:41:25,390
On what conditions will you be willing to help me?

591
00:41:28,430 --> 00:41:31,550
I won't lend it to you no matter what.

592
00:41:31,910 --> 00:41:34,080
Hey... Hey!

593
00:41:34,100 --> 00:41:36,010
You tell me, you two,

594
00:41:36,030 --> 00:41:38,070
