595
00:41:38,090 --> 00:41:40,960
Didn't I tell you to take good care of your skin?

596
00:41:40,990 --> 00:41:43,410
Look at you. You must have not slept well last night, right?

597
00:41:43,410 --> 00:41:45,730
Your black eye circles have all come out.

598
00:41:45,750 --> 00:41:47,030
Don't say anything anymore.

599
00:41:47,060 --> 00:41:48,200
I will not listen to you.

600
00:41:48,200 --> 00:41:50,320
Just let me die.

601
00:41:50,690 --> 00:41:53,780
Hey... stop mentioning death.

602
00:41:53,790 --> 00:41:55,220
Who doesn't know how to die?

603
00:41:55,220 --> 00:41:57,210
A person should live with a bit of meaning.

604
00:41:57,210 --> 00:41:59,660
If I am like you choosing to die every time I encounter a problem,

605
00:41:59,680 --> 00:42:01,740
I would have died a hundred times.

606
00:42:01,750 --> 00:42:04,170
Stop your nonsense! Just kill me!

607
00:42:04,180 --> 00:42:06,910
You are just young but you have such a bad temper.

608
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:09,580
Always getting angry will make you age fast.

609
00:42:09,620 --> 00:42:13,100
You should try smiling more.

610
00:42:15,570 --> 00:42:19,170
You're even lecturing me? Don't you also want to escape?

611
00:42:19,190 --> 00:42:21,180
Fallacy.

612
00:42:22,770 --> 00:42:26,990
No one is hindering or stopping you, yet you still stay on this island.

613
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:30,880
You even have the nerve to scold these people who want to die?

614
00:42:34,630 --> 00:42:37,300
Every person has their predicaments.

615
00:42:37,300 --> 00:42:41,450
